-- New Cotai Announces Macao Studio City Suit, ESun Says; Can't Confirm Writ
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-14T14:43:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-14/new-cotai-announces-macao-studio-city-suit-esun-says-can-t-confirm-writ.html
ESun Holdings Ltd.  and  CapitaLand
Ltd.  are aware New Cotai Entertainment LLC has announced it has
started legal proceedings in Hong Kong in relation to the Macao
Studio City project, eSun said in an e-mailed statement.  East Asia Satellite Television (Holdings) Ltd., the project
company in which eSun owns 40 percent and CapitaLand 20 percent,
and CapitaLand have received letters demanding immediate steps
to execute New Cotai’s casino lease, today’s e-mail said.  Both eSun and East Asia Satellite are reviewing the letters
with the lawyers and are preparing a response, according to the
e-mail. Neither company has received any writ of summons, nor
can confirm whether New Cotai has started legal proceedings.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  